<subSubSection pageId="41" pageNumber="42" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="41.[151,1437,1792,1999]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,322,1900,1927]" pageId="41" pageNumber="42">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
Interstriae 10 sharply elevated to near apex. Protibiae with an additional mesal tooth. Pronotum strongly asperate. Elytra with erect setae on odd-numbered interstriae. Female frons with small circular ring of incurved setae. Not similar to other known species.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
